          "type": "text",
          "text": "USP_AccountBillingAvailableByInvoiceBillingGroupRetrieve",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve available account billing records that are associated with a specific invoice and billing group. It filters out billing records that are already linked to an invoice and returns detailed billing information. Additionally, it logs the operation's execution details, including any exceptions encountered during the process."
        }
